module.exports = inverse

/**
 * Returns the inverse of the components of a vec2
 *
 * @param {vec2} out the receiving vector
 * @param {vec2} a vector to invert
 * @returns {vec2} out
 */
function inverse(out, a) {
  out[0] = 1.0 / a[0]
  out[1] = 1.0 / a[1]
  return out
}
